sentences: Over several years, he has created artwork for the classic argentinean band Rata Blanca including the cover of the album Tormenta El√©ctrica.

In recent years, he has created art inspired by the world of the paranormal, working independently, as well as professionally on book covers for leading cryptozoology researchers such as Lyle Blackburn and Loren Coleman.
In 2017, AFM Records commissioned the album cover of Phoenix, the return of the Swedish band Nocturnal Rites.
Also during 2017, the British heavy metal band Judas Priest entrusted him with the creation of the cover artwork of their new album Firepower, released on March 9 of 2018.
